  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\nSee issue marked with \"2\": Avatar next to the message is shown on the same line as username while in designs it's shown on the same line as the last line of the message\r\n![img_1976](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6584810/37472195-c6ea6ae8-286b-11e8-8ca1-7d90cced11c7.jpg)\r\n\r\ndesign\r\n<img width=\"377\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-03-15 at 15 29 03\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6584810/37472281-f9492af6-286b-11e8-9109-b7cc402b575e.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Open 1:1 chat \r\n- Send some message that is 2-3 lines long and check where is your avatar displayed \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: PR-3255\r\n* Operating System: Android and iOS\r\n",
